   About Bouygues

   Founded by Francis Bouygues in 1952, Bouygues is a diversified group
   with a strong corporate culture. Its businesses focus on three sectors:
   construction, with Bouygues Construction (building, civil works, energy
   and services), Bouygues Immobilier (property) and Colas (roads),
   telecoms with Bouygues Telecom and media with TF1.
